       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. SANCBAT2.
      * SANCTIONS-FEED INTAKE FOR THE TWO MANDATED UNSC SOURCES.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY UNSCREG2.
       01  WS-RECORD-COUNT PIC 9(6) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-BATCH-ROUTE  PIC X(6) VALUE 'HOLD'.
       01  WS-SCREEN-COUNT PIC 9(6) VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-LIST-SOURCE
           ACCEPT WS-RECORD-COUNT
           PERFORM 2000-ROUTE-FEED
           DISPLAY 'ROUTE: ' WS-BATCH-ROUTE
           DISPLAY 'SCREENED: ' WS-SCREEN-COUNT
           STOP RUN.
       2000-ROUTE-FEED.
           IF MANDATED-SANCTIONS-FEED
              MOVE WS-RECORD-COUNT TO WS-SCREEN-COUNT
              MOVE 'SCREEN' TO WS-BATCH-ROUTE
           ELSE
              MOVE 'HOLD' TO WS-BATCH-ROUTE
           END-IF.
